  • Job Search Platforms: Use filters like "immediate hire," "urgent," or "start immediately" on sites like Indeed, LinkedIn, and Glassdoor.

  • Staffing Agencies: Register with agencies that specialize in quick placements.

  • Company Websites: Some companies advertise rapid hiring events or walk-in interviews on their career pages.
